          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">institution</ENAMEX> and randomly selected <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> of these <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">states</ENAMEX> from each <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">zone</ENAMEX>. To obtain a
