          Testing and Consent
          
            Practices
            <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">Seventeen percent</NUMEX> of surveyed health-care <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">professionals</ENAMEX> reported that their facility
            had a written <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">HIV</ENAMEX> testing policy (<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table 3</ENAMEX>). <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Respondents</ENAMEX> indicated that the policies
